🎙️ [SPORT] | Neuer responds to Ter Stegen: &quot;I don't know if that's good for the group.&quot;<br />
<br />
🔊Neuer: &quot;It's not the first time that Ter Stegen said this, I am a team player, and I always think the good of the team, I'm happy with how I am playing. I can't say anything else. &quot;

Griezmann: &quot;It's my second month at Bar&ccedil;a and I have to get used to the movements of Messi, Su&aacute;rez and Demb&eacute;l&eacute; - and they to mine.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;Playing away from home is always different. The opposition play with more confidence, they demand more from us. We have to create more chances and improve.&quot;

ter Stegen: &quot;People know what I am capable of doing. I trust myself and today was the occasion to prove it.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;We have played a good game although there are aspects to improve. We get a point that I think is fair for both teams.&quot;
